Project Name : AWS Static Website Hosting

Objective  : To host a static website on AWS using Amazon S3 and make it accessible through a public URL.

Services Used

* Amazon S3
* Static Website Hosting

Procedure

1. Created an S3 bucket.
2. Enabled Static Website Hosting.
3. Uploaded website files (index.html and related files).
4. Configured bucket permissions for public access.
5. Generated the website endpoint URL.
6. Tested website accessibility through a browser.

